   <taskbody>
      <prereq class="- topic/section task/prereq ">
         <ul class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Notifications templates are configured for the form in the workflow stage when the notifications is being initiated. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on configuring email templates, refer to <xref href="../../Administration/Configuration_Toolkit/Workflow_Management/CreateWFSimple.dita"
                        class="- topic/xref ">Configuring Ball in Court Notifications .</xref>
               </ph>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </prereq>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">You can share form information with a user invited to the project but not have access to the form or not be a stakeholder at the workflow stage of the form when the notification is being initiated.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">On initiating a Ball in Court notification, an email is sent to the recipient and thenotification is saved in the<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">INBOX</uicontrol>page of the recipient.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The following procedure uses the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Expenses</uicontrol> form as an example to describe the procedure to initiatethe Ball in Court notification.</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step product="Project_Module" class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Projects</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step product="Planning_Module" class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planning</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step product="Planning_Module" class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Planned Projects</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">PLANNED PROJECTS</uicontrol>list page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the list page, double-click the required project.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, expand the project folder, expand the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Commitments &amp; Expenses</uicontrol> folder, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Expenses Form</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">New</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Miscellaneous Expenses</uicontrol>, specify the expense details, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select the saved form, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Edit</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Ball in Court</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The feature is available only if the form is in the workflow stage for which a template is selected in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Ball In Court Request Email Template</uicontrol> list in the workflow definition of the form. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on configuring email templates, refer to <xref href="../../Administration/Configuration_Toolkit/Workflow_Management/CreateWFSimple.dita"
                        class="- topic/xref ">Configuring Ball in Court Notifications </xref>
               </ph>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">From the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Route To</uicontrol> drop-down list, select the user to share the information of the required form.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">Available options are users invited to the project.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Notes</uicontrol> box, enter any notes to be sent to the recipient.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Set Days To Complete for Next Stage</uicontrol> box, enter the number of days by when the task must be completed.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">OK</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">A notification email is sent to the recipient, and a notification is saved in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">INBOX</uicontrol> page of the user. 
<p class="- topic/p ">The recipient can now respond to the Ball in Court notification.
</p>
               <p class="- topic/p ">Information that is shared is based on the template selected in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Ball In Court Request Email Template</uicontrol> list in the workflow definition of the form.</p>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
